{"tid":2198294,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"蔡英文：台灣主權寸步不讓　民主自由堅守不退","createTime":"2020-09-11T09:02:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-11T09:02:35.000Z","uid":241764,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a6adabba9dd2f953e56c4f2cfd31f654b69b86fe","tid":2198294,"uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T09:02:35.000Z","msg":"蔡英文今日視察兩處「空軍防空飛彈連」，她表示，解放軍軍機近日在台灣附近的軍事演習相當頻繁，各種防空的假訊息亦很多，相信官兵在任務中，都很清楚這些情況，亦了解責任非常重大。她指示官兵必須24小時配合輪班，保持戰備狀態，不僅要緊盯雷達監測，掌握情報及資訊，更要隨機應變。<br />\n<br />\n全文: <a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1549101-20200911.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1549101-20200911.htm&d=lPOaXpfFeUboYNX3auI3fiZO8jd1M6XCUNMtuDfdPZA%3D&h=f5f4030c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1549101-20200911.htm&h=81083bf2\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1549101-20200911.htm</a>"}]}